Radios:
	Needs to un-select itself after a tap
	Needs to update the selected value in the root
	Support a hook to do something on selection

Sliders:
	Render the left/right image

Sections:
	Support for rendering icons

Widgets:
	Support checkbox (more than one item checked)
	Image Chooser
	Text Entry
	Password Entry

Reflection binder:
	Create the Element tree and then set the values back after editing.